00:00:04.819 --> 00:00:10.559
How to improve the usability of a website?

00:00:10.559 --> 00:00:15.259
What is usability? Usability is a concept
that characterizes the overall user-friendly

00:00:15.259 --> 00:00:19.890
interface, intuitive navigation and access
to information on the website. You need to

00:00:19.890 --> 00:00:24.700
remember the following factors to achieve
a high level of usability.

00:00:24.700 --> 00:00:25.700
